'''Bom Jesus Basilica'''-ak Saint Francis Xavier Shrine munttat. Ye igroz Odlem Goeant asa, ani tacho retor (''rector'') asa Fr. Savio Barreto, SJ.He igorz ek UNESCO heritage site zaun asa.He igorz 24th November,1594 ant baandhunh shuru kelele ani 15th May 1605aant baandhuun jaale.He igorz aak,1946 aant Minor basilica ache naav dile.He igorz ak Bom Jesus munthath. Heze arthe boro [[Jezu]] ya balok jezu asa konak he igorz somorphan kyeala.He igorz aant Sant Francis Xavier aache kudd aasa<ref>bomjesus.org/history</ref>.
He igorz,sogle barathana ani Goen purant igorzasoon ek jaaoon aasa.He igorz Borque architecture aache bore udaharan jaaoon aasa.Heeze dharneenth marble asoon kaylae ani thode keemthe phatore bhi aasa.He igorz aache altaar mast sobeet aasa kintu igorz aache bitheriala doosre bhaag maast saral asa.He igorz aant Saant Francis Xavier aache jeevan aasun vibhiin chitran aasa.Saant Francis Xavier aache kuud altaar aache voir aasa ani ek ‘silver casket’ aache bhiter aasa.He ‘casket’ Medicis aache aintim raaja, Cosimo III, the Grand Duke of Tuscany aan igorzek dilie.
==Itihaas ani Mahatva==
[[Image:Mausoléo São Francisco Xavier.jpg|thumb|Relics of St. Francis Xavier]]
[[File:Goa - St. Francis Xavier's Church.JPG|thumb|The ornamented entrance to the church.]]
Saant Francis Xavier China aak vitanaar sarlo aani thezo shareer aak thoich daphaan kele.Kintu don varsa nantar thezo shareer aak Goen haadle, thezhe eecha prokor, aani Sam Paul aache igorz aant dorele.Saant Francis Xavier 1662 aant canonize jaale uprant , thezo sharer aak Bom Jezucha igorzant dorele aani he aatha thanka thoich aasa<ref>daily.bhaskar.com/news/TRA-7-unknown-facts-about-the-400-years-old-bom-jesus-church-in-india-4757808-NOR.html</ref>.
He igorz kristaov loog aak bhari mahatv dorita keithyak monje he igarz aant Saant Francis aache kuud aasa. He kuud prati dha varshant , Saant Francis Xavier aache janam divasaacha vailar,soogle loog aak(kristov aani dooshre dharma aache loog aak) dhakoonk sakla haadta.He kuud aak paloonk sogle kadent soon lok yetat. He kuud aache ninthe mast lokank archrya bogne malyea.
==2014 che exposition==
He vars(2014), Saant Francis Xavier aache kudd 22nd November aasoon 4th January, 2015 taanka exposition aak aasa. He kudd aache exposition ek meese aason shuru kalea.He meesant Mangaluru aacho Bishop Aloysius D’Zouzaan mukhya betonedar alselo.<ref> Times of India, 23 November 2014, Thousands venerate sacred relics</ref>
